	<h3><em><strong>Latin: "I discover, I find"</strong></em></h3>

	<p>Invenio is a collection of peer-reviewed scientific data in a decentralized database. Researchers can submit papers to be reviewed, rated, and used by their peers. To ensure quality posts and reviews, Invenio implements a reputation system determined by fellow scientists; the summative rating controls the influence of individual researches on Invenio. Overall, Invenio is a unique platform for scientists and researchers to expand their thinking and validate the work of their peers on a collaborative website.</p>
